"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(re)

any assistance given in accordance with the Carer’s Assistance (Young Carer Grants) (Scotland) Regulations 2019;
"""

person_is_given_assistance:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

given_assistance_is_in_accordance_with_the_carers_assistance_young_carer_grants_scotland_regulations_2019:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

assistance_given_in_accordance_with_the_carers_assistance_young_carer_grants_scotland_regulations_2019_is_excepted_from_prescribed_social_security_benefits_15_1_re:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        person_is_given_assistance and given_assistance_is_in_accordance_with_the_carers_assistance_young_carer_grants_scotland_regulations_2019
